      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities must be conducted on a geometry and flow regime sufficiently similar to the COU device and operating conditions to support extrapolation of credibility.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump, which shares impeller topology and operating range with the CPB device under assessment. Flow regime (turbulent, Re ~ 10^4) is consistent. Validation activities are judged directly relevant to the COU at Gradation 2."
    },
    {
