      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence and round-off error need not be explicitly quantified at MRL 2 Gradation 1 provided solver residuals are reported.",
      "rationale": "At MRL 2, Gradation 1 for numerical solver error is acceptable. Residuals monitored to 10^-5 for continuity and momentum; no divergence observed. Explicit iterative error quantification not required at this risk level."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
