      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2 Gradation 1, a documented simulation plan reviewed by a second analyst is sufficient; formal use-error quantification is not required.",
      "rationale": "Simulation plan documented and reviewed by a second CFD analyst prior to execution. Boundary condition inputs verified against experimental test report. Gradation 1 use-error criterion satisfied without formal sensitivity analysis."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
