      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2 Gradation 1, experimental sample characterization must confirm use of appropriate blood analog and pump specimen; statistical characterization of sample variability is not required.",
      "rationale": "FDA generic pump specimen confirmed as machined to published CAD tolerances. Blood analog (glycerol-water, 36% v/v) characterized for viscosity and density prior to testing. Sample-level statistical variability assessment not required at Gradation 1."
    },
