      "acceptanceCriteria": "At MRL 2 Gradation 1, a qualitative argument that simulation input parameters match experimental conditions is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Simulation boundary conditions set to match experimentally measured inlet flow rates and pump rotational speeds. Qualitative equivalency confirmed by comparison table in the V&V report. Gradation 1 criterion satisfied."
