    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018. Discretization error is within 5% GCI, output comparison yields 11.4% mean absolute error within experimental uncertainty, and validation activities are directly relevant to the CPB COU. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 acceptance criterion is supported by the credibility evidence. The assessment team concludes the model is sufficiently credible for the stated context of use.",
